extendedInfo.description: The Focus iCare app contains the latest information about eye care. It has the following features: * Wiki (learn all about your eye) * Eye care videos (watch informational videos about eye health and eye care products) * Eye care news (the latest news in eye care) * Reorder contacts * Driving directions & contact information for Focus iCareTags:Patricia ShustockJulia GarrMichael MullerWashington, DCVision Source
